description:
Miracle Escape

Aired on 04/15/2007, Narrated by Jonathan Aris.

On 2 August 2005, Air France Flight 358, an Airbus A340-300, overruns the runway while attempting to land in a storm. The Airbus A340 travels through the airport perimeter fence into a small ravine and catches fire. All 309 passengers and crew survived.
